I pretended everything was...

01:13:30.062 --> 01:13:31.928
fine.

01:13:31.930 --> 01:13:35.166
But I can't pretend anymore.
I can't.

01:13:35.168 --> 01:13:37.400
- Paul...
- Listen to me.

01:13:37.402 --> 01:13:40.236
