I didn't tell you,

01:14:30.756 --> 01:14:34.460
but I got a call
the other day from Rachel Ray.

01:14:36.461 --> 01:14:38.762
Oh.

01:14:38.764 --> 01:14:42.733
What's she like?
I hear she's really nice.

01:14:42.735 --> 01:14:44.200
No, not from her.

01:14:44.202 --> 01:14:47.337
