"ski in, ski out."

01:15:37.255 --> 01:15:40.923
I'll be there Friday.
No, I can't come Thursday.

01:15:40.925 --> 01:15:42.993
I've got to see my lawyer.

01:15:42.995 --> 01:15:46.163
Oh, just stupid stuff.

01:15:46.165 --> 01:15:49.266
Yeah. You can have
