and that probably happened.

01:22:40.512 --> 01:22:42.579
I could make some sushi.
I did train

01:22:42.581 --> 01:22:45.716
with one of the world's
leading sushi chefs.

01:22:45.718 --> 01:22:47.551
That was at a demo
at Williams-Sonoma

01:22:47.553 --> 01:22:49.352
