I was with you.

01:22:49.354 --> 01:22:54.490
You know, your version
of events is so pedestrian.

01:22:54.492 --> 01:22:56.193
Also known as reality.

01:22:56.195 --> 01:22:58.061
Blah, blah, blah, blah,
blah, blah, blah.

01:22:58.063 --> 01:23:00.663
